Comment: 0,0:02:05.54,0:03:22.95,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:12.67,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}きっと そう 僕たちは太古の時代から
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:12.67,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}我们一定自太古时代起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:19.97,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}引き寄せられる運命だったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:19.97,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}便命中注定被彼此吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:23.89,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}宇宙は知ってただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:23.89,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}宇宙应该早已知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:28.23,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}地球の愛の誕生を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:28.23,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}地球上爱会诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:36.11,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}深い海の底 一つの命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:36.11,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}深海之底的一个生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:39.11,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}「あの光は何?」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:39.11,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}「那束光芒是什么?」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:43.20,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}これから未来がどうなるか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:43.20,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}未来的路将如何展开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:46.75,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}誰にも分からないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:46.75,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}无人知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:50.75,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}それでも どこかに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:50.75,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}即便如此 在某处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:54.59,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}いつも光が見えてきたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:54.59,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}也总能看见光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:58.30,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}それは遠い宇宙からの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:58.30,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}仿佛是来自遥远星辰的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:02.05,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}希望のような星の輝き
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:02.05,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}宛如希望的璀璨光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:06.10,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}何を語っているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:06.10,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}它究竟在诉说着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.89,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}夜明けまでは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.89,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}直到破晓前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:15.90,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}夢を 覚めるな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:15.90,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}愿梦永不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:22.95,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}「あの光は何?」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:22.95,OP-zh,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}「那束光芒是什么?」
Comment: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:22.95,OP-ja,,0,0,0,,OP end
